{"lastModified":1775745995623,"uri":"c::9938368400::vessel::d5cca497-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece - Aegean/Cyclades Sea, Greece - Ionian Sea\n\nAgata Blu, a Sunreef 70, strikes the perfect balance between extraordinary comfort, impressive sailing performance, and cutting-edge technology. Designed with spacious living areas, this fully customized yacht offers a contemporary interior and a seamless connection between indoor and outdoor spaces.\n\nAccommodating guests in four beautifully designed staterooms with additional pullout beds for children, Agata Blu ensures both luxury and practicality. The yacht’s hull and superstructure have been masterfully crafted to maximize living space while maintaining exceptional seaworthiness, making her an outstanding choice for a charter adventure.\n\nThe flybridge spans an impressive 50 square meters, offering a spacious retreat for relaxation and social gatherings. The expansive bow section features dedicated lounging and sunbathing areas, providing the perfect setting to soak in breathtaking views.\n\nWith her remarkable design and luxurious amenities, Agata Blu is the ideal yacht for an unforgettable charter experience on the water.","blueprint":{"name":"AGATA BLU","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca497-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::60ff9441-00e1-11f1-a935-7950e57cb1b6/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca497-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::60fe0da0-00e1-11f1-a935-7950e57cb1b6/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca497-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::60fea9e1-00e1-11f1-a935-7950e57cb1b6/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca497-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::61005790-00e1-11f1-a935-7950e57cb1b6/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca497-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::60ff9440-00e1-11f1-a935-7950e57cb1b6/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel: